b(0, 159, 78);\">读写分离</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：将读操作和写操作分配给不同的节点处理，提高系统稳定性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">提升读取性能</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提高数据的查询效率。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">没有容错和恢复的能力</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">存在单点故障</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">：一旦Master节点故障，不会自动选出新的主节点，导致后续所有的写操作直接失败。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">可用性低</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">：主节点故障时不能自动实现故障转移，需要人工干预手动切换，故障恢复时间长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">没有实现数据分片</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">无法在线扩容</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">单个主节点承担所有写操作</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的应用场景」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">适用于数据备份、读写分离、对可用性要求不高，小规模数据处理的场景。</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471443.png\" width=\"678\" height=\"367\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">哨</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">兵（Sentinel）模式</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的原理」</span></strong><br/></section><section><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;\">哨兵模式是在Redis主从集群的基础上加入了哨兵节点，监控主节点和从节点的状态。当Master节点出现故障时，哨兵节点会</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">自动从剩余的Slave节点中选举出一个新的Master节点</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，并通知其他Slave节点和客户端。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">&nbsp;高可用性</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：提供故障的自动处理能力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">&nbsp;容灾恢复</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在主从模式数据备份的基础上，提供容错和自动恢复机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>读写分离</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提升读取性能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>解决了单点故障</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：监测到master节点故障，会自动从slave节点中选出一个节点将其切换成master节点，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">在选举结束之前，redis会开启保护机制，禁止写操作</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，直到新的master节点产生。每个哨兵节点都是一个独立的进程，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">哨兵节点之间也会互相监控</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">1. 依然没有实现数据分片，无法在线扩容，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2. 每个从节点和主节点的耦合度高，在主节点宕机到重新选举Master的期间，服务不可用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">3. 集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;单个主节点承担所有写操作，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的应用场景」</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">适用于数据备份、容灾恢复，高可用性、小规模数据处理的场景。</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471444.png\" width=\"678\" height=\"248\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: 248px;\"/></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">集</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">群（Cluster）模式</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 171, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">「Cluster的原理」</span></strong></section><section><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在Redis Cluster中，引入slot槽来实现数据分片，slot的整体取值范围是0~16383，每个节点会分配一个slot区间，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">数据分散在多个节点上。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">每个分片都是由一个Redis主机和多个从机组成</span></strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">分片和分片之间是相互平行的</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">每个master节点负责维护一部分槽</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">以及</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">槽所映射的键值数据</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在Redis Cluster中，数据被分为<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">16384个槽，每个槽存储一部分数据。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 140, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">数据分片</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">是用CRC16算法对key进行hash操作，哈希计算的结果是16位的哈希值，将哈希值对16384取模，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">得到槽位编号。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">当存取Key的时候，根据<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: left;\">槽位编号，</span>找到对应的节</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">点进行数据的读写。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 171, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">「Cluster的优点」</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">数据分片</span></strong>：<span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">基于slot槽的数据分片</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">，突破单节点的内存限制，</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">实现更大规模的数据分布式存储。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>横向扩展</strong></span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">：实现在线动态横向扩缩容。<br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>高可用性</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">：每个分片都是一个主节点对应多</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.034em; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">个从节点，主从复制，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.034em; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">当Master出现故障，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">会从Slave节点中选举一个新的Master继续提供服务，实现自动故障转移。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 171, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">「Cluster的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">1. slave节点只是一个冷备节点，用于在主节点故障时接替其角色，不提供分担读操作的压力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2. 对Redis里面的批量操作指令会有限制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Pin