ng: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">」</span></strong>基于slot槽的数据分片<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">，突破单节点的内存限制，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">实现更大规模的数据分布式存储</span>，提供了高可用性和<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">在线动态横向扩容</span>的能力，提升数据的读写性能</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">，主要针对于</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">海量数据</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">+高并发+高可用</span></strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">的场景。</span></section><section><br/></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">从集群架构上来说：<br/></span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">哨兵(Sentinel)模式</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">中心化</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的集群实现方案，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong>一主多从</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">集群(Cluster)模式</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去中心化</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的集群实现方案，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong>多主多从</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></section><section><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></section><section><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">主从模式和哨兵模式每个节点存储的都是全量的数据，当存储的数据量过大时，就需要对数据进行分片后存储到多个redis实例上。此时就要用到Redis Sharding技术。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">如果数据量很大，那么建议就用cluster。数据量不是很大时，使用sentinel就够了。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><br/></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; letter-spacing: 2px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">Redis集群分片的方式<br/></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.<strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「客户端分片<strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">」</span></strong></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">分片逻辑在Redis客户端实现，采用一致性哈希来决定Redis节点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">优点：不依赖于第三方中间件，服务端的Redis实例彼此独立，相互无关联，分片逻辑和路由规则可控。</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">缺点：这是一种静态的分片方案，增删Redis节点时需要手工调整分片程序，服务端Redis集群拓扑结构有变化时，每个客户端都需要更新调整，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">运维成本较高。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.</span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「中间件分片<strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">」</span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Redis客户端把请求发送到中间件（例如Twemproxy、Codis），借助中间件实现Redis节点的路由分派，根据路由规则将请求发送到正确的Redis节点上。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">优点：支持平滑增减Redis实例而无需修改任何的代码。</span></p><p><br/></p><section><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">缺点：</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">每个请求都经过代理才能到达Redis服务器，过程中产生性能损失。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-spacing: 2px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「客户端服务端分片<strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">」</span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Redis Cluster模式，客户端采用一致性哈希，服务端提供错误节点的重定向服务。</span></p>', 'uploads/img/2023-10/b040760f1a180ed3a86b75402ff72a1f.jpg', 'uploads/thumb/2023-10/fd824a7df6cbf2f2875eb2d6b2ea56e6.jpg', '', '8', '0', '0', '1', '1', '100', '5,3', '1697471411', '1717080533');
INSERT INTO `cy_article` VALUES ('40', '2', '0', '0', 'admin', 'PHP 8.3新功能全解析，必备的开发利器，赶紧收藏！', '', 'PHP 8.3新功能全解析，必备的开发利器，赶紧收藏！', 'PHP 8.3新功能全解析，必备的开发利器，赶紧收藏！', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在PHP可以轻松地使用原生PHP进行桌面编程。当然，以前有许多其他工具可用于在桌面编程中使用PHP，但我觉得原生PHP比它们更酷。无论如何，让我们开始深入了解我们的功能。</p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 10px;\">JSON验证</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在开发新项目时，我们经常需要验证字符串是否为JSON。现在，PHP添加了一个本地方法来验证字符串是否为JSON。这个功能真的很酷。例如，我们可以这样使用它：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$json</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(152, 195, 121); line-height: 26px;\">&#39;{&nbsp;&quot;example&quot;:&nbsp;&quot;title&quot;&nbsp;}&#39;</span>;<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$is_json</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(86, 182, 194); line-height: 26px;\">false</span>;<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">if</span>&nbsp;(json_validate(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$json</span>))&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;有效的JSON<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$is_json</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(86, 182, 194); line-height: 26px;\">true</span>;<br/>}<br/><br/>//&nbsp;或者更好的方法<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$is_json</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;json_validate(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$json</span>);<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前，大多数PHP程序员使用<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">json_decode()</code>函数来执行此任务，但这会使用不必要的内存和处理能力来检查有效性。实际上，验证JSON字符串并不需要使用<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">json_decode</code>。</p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 10px;\">改进的unserialize()错误处理</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">unserialize()</code>目前在处理错误时缺乏一致性，它可能生成<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">E_NOTICE、E_WARNING</code>，甚至根据输入字符串的格式错误抛出不可预测的Exception或Error。但是，新的PHP功能将解决这个问题。下面是一个示例：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在建议的之前，我们在PHP中处理反序列化错误的过程可能类似于以下内容：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\">try&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;set_error_handler(static&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$severity</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$message</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$file</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$line</span>)&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;throw&nbsp;\\ErrorException(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$message</span>,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$severity</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$file</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$line</span>);<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;});<br/><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$result</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;unserialize(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$serialized</span>);<br/>}&nbsp;catch&nbsp;(\\Throwable&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$e</span>)&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;如果要处理非序列化错误，可选的catch代码块。<br/>}&nbsp;finally&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;restore_error_handler();<br/>}<br/><br/>var_dump(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$result</span>);<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这个新功能之后，我们可以这样使用<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">unserialize()</code>函数：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;unserialize(string&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$data</span>,&nbsp;array&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$options</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;[]):&nbsp;mixed<br/>{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;try&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;现有的非列化逻辑在这里发生。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;catch&nbsp;(\\Throwable&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$e</span>)&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;throw&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\UnserializationFailedException(previous:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$e</span>);<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br/>}<br/>并且UnserializationFailedException的实现如下：<br/><br/>class&nbsp;UnserializationFailedException&nbsp;extends&nbsp;\\Exception<br/>{<br/>}<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这真是超级酷！</p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 10px;\">动态提取类常量</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8.3之前，我们不能通过变量获取基于类的常量。当我们调用它们时，应该直接添加常量名。但在8.3中，我们可以使用变量来提取常量。下面是一个示例：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\">class&nbsp;StatusCodes&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;OK&nbsp;=&nbsp;200;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;NOT_FOUND&nbsp;=&nbsp;404;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;INTERNAL_ERROR&nbsp;=&nbsp;500;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;UNAUTHORIZED&nbsp;=&nbsp;401;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;FORBIDDEN&nbsp;=&nbsp;403;<br/>}<br/><br/>//&nbsp;访问常量<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">echo</span>&nbsp;StatusCodes::OK;&nbsp;//&nbsp;输出:&nbsp;200<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">echo</span>&nbsp;StatusCodesNOT_FOUND;&nbsp;//&nbsp;输出:&nbsp;404<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">echo</span>&nbsp;StatusCodes::INTERNAL_ERROR;&nbsp;//&nbsp;输出:&nbsp;500<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">echo</span>&nbsp;StatusCodes::UNAUTHORIZED;&nbsp;//&nbsp;输出:&nbsp;401<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">echo</span>&nbsp;StatusCodes::FORBIDDEN;&nbsp;//&nbsp;输出:&nbsp;403<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这样，我们可以动态地从类中调用常量，我真的很喜欢这个功能。</p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 10px;\">引入只读修改</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个提案的目标是克服只读属性在深度克隆时的限制。在8.3之前，只读属性在<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">__clone()</code>魔法方法调用范围内不能重新初始化。但是在8.3之后，我们可以在<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(19, 148, 216); background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); word-break: normal;\">__clone</code>方法中重新初始化只读属性。下面是一个示例：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8.3之前：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\">class&nbsp;Example&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">readonly</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$readOnlyProp</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(152, 195, 121); line-height: 26px;\">&#39;初始值&#39;</span>;<br/>}<br/><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$instance</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;Example();<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$instance</span>-&gt;readOnlyProp&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(152, 195, 121); line-height: 26px;\">&#39;New&nbsp;Value&#39;</span>;&nbsp;//&nbsp;这行不通<br/><br/>class&nbsp;Example&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;__construct(<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">readonly</span>&nbsp;string&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$readOnly</span>,<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)&nbsp;{}<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 174, 238); line-height: 26px;\">__clone</span></span>()<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;readOnlyProp&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">clone</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;readOnlyProp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;不起作用会出现错误。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br/>}<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8.3之后：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\">class&nbsp;Foo&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;__construct(<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">readonly</span>&nbsp;string&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$example</span>,<br/>&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">readonly</span>&nbsp;string&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$foo</span><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)&nbsp;{}<br/><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 174, 238); line-height: 26px;\">__clone</span></span>()<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;example&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">clone</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;example;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Works.<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;cloneFoo();<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br/><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(198, 120, 221); line-height: 26px;\">function</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 174, 238); line-height: 26px;\">cloneFoo</span></span>()<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">unset</span>(<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$this</span>-&gt;foo);&nbsp;//&nbsp;也可以使用<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br/>}<br/><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$foo</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;Foo(<span style=\"color: rgb(152, 195, 121); line-height: 26px;\">&#39;Test&#39;</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(152, 195, 121); line-height: 26px;\">&#39;Example&#39;</span>);<br/><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$foo2</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 192, 123); line-height: 26px;\">clone</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$foo</span>;<br/>//&nbsp;没有错误，Foo2::<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$example</span>被深度克隆，而Foo2::<span style=\"color: rgb(209, 154, 102); line-height: 26px;\">$foo</span>变为未初始化。<br/></code></pre><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border-left: 4px solid; padding-left: 10px;\">类型化常量</span></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8.3之前，我们定义常量时没有指定类型。但是在8.3之后，我们可以为类常量指定类型。下面是一个示例：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; overflow: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><code style=\"font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; display: -webkit-box; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px 16px 16px; color: rgb(171, 178, 191); background: rgb(40, 44, 52); border-radius: 5px;\">class&nbsp;Example<br/>{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;const&nbsp;HTTP_STATUS_OK:int&nbsp;=&nbsp;200;<br/>}<br/></code></pre><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 2; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些是PHP的一些酷炫功能，让桌面编程更加简单和有趣。现在你可以尝试使用这些新功能来提升你的编程体验。祝你好运</p>', 'uploads/images/202312/659139d088e3a.jpg', 'uploads/thumb/202312/20231231659139d0d3e9d.jpeg', '', '1', '0', '0', '1', '1', '100', '5,4,3', '1699103201', '1717079568');
INSERT INTO `cy_article` VALUES ('41', '3', '0', '0', 'admin', '详解Redis集群的三种实现方案', '', '详解Redis集群的三种实现方案', '详解Redis集群的三种实现方案', '<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471442.jpeg\" width=\"678\" height=\"577\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: auto !important;\"/></span></p><blockquote style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px; outline: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.4); color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: inherit; overflow: auto; text-size-adjust: inherit; line-height: 1.55em; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.1);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.9em; outline: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">Redis分布式存储的常见方案有：<br/></span></p><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">1.「主从 (Master-Slave) 模式</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>主从复制，读写分离，数据备份。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">2.「哨兵 (Sentinel) 模式</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>一主多从，哨兵监控，自动处理故障，容错和恢复。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">3.「&nbsp;集群 (Cluster) 模式</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>多主多从，数据分片，在线扩容。</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br/></span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">Redis集群切片的方式有：</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">1.「客户端分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">分片逻辑在Redis客户端实现，采用一致性哈希来决定Redis节点。</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">2.「中间件分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">借助中间件实现Redis节点的路由分派，根据路由规则将请求发送到正确的Redis节点上。</span></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">3.&nbsp;「客户端服务端分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Redis Cluster模式，客户端采用一致性哈希，服务端提供错误节点的重定向服务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span></p><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">本文将详细介绍「Redis分布式存储</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">」<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">的3种方案</span></span>和「Redis集群切片<span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>的3种常见方式。</span></span></section></blockquote><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\">什<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">么是Redis集群</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">Redis集群是由多个redis实例组成的集合，将缓存的数据分散到多个redis节点上存储，减轻单个缓存节点的访问压力，达到分流效果，提高了存储容量和吞吐量，提供高可用性和容错恢复能力，实现了水平扩容。</span></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\">R<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">edis<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">集群的作用和优势</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">处理大规模数据</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">：<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">将数据分散在多个节点上，从而突破单节点内存限制，有效应对数据量的增长和高并发的访问请求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">高可用性</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">：<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">当主节点发生故障时，集群会自动选举新的主节点，从而实现故障转移，保证高可用性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">可扩展性</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">：Redis集群可以根据业务需求和系统负载，动态添加或删除节点，实现水平扩展，以适应数据规模的变化。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">高性能</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：Redis集群中的各个节点可以并行处理不同的请求，从而提高系统整体吞吐量和响应速度，适合于高并发访问的场景。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动故障转移</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：Redis集群通过哨兵节点监控主节点的健康状态，在主节点故障时，自动选举新的主节点，减少服务中断和数据丢失的风险。</span></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">主</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">从（Master - Slave）模式</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的原理」</span></strong></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">主从模式是指在Redis集群中有</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">一个主节点(Master)和多个从节点(Slave)。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">Master节点负责数据的写操作，Slave节点负责数据的读操作。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过主从复制，将Master节点的数据变更同步到Slave节点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">数据备份</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：通过主从复制，从节点备份主节点的数据，提高数据可靠性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">读写分离</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：将读操作和写操作分配给不同的节点处理，提高系统稳定性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">提升读取性能</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提高数据的查询效率。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">没有容错和恢复的能力</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">存在单点故障</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">：一旦Master节点故障，不会自动选出新的主节点，导致后续所有的写操作直接失败。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">可用性低</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">：主节点故障时不能自动实现故障转移，需要人工干预手动切换，故障恢复时间长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">没有实现数据分片</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">无法在线扩容</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">单个主节点承担所有写操作</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的应用场景」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">适用于数据备份、读写分离、对可用性要求不高，小规模数据处理的场景。</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471443.png\" width=\"678\" height=\"367\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">哨</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">兵（Sentinel）模式</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的原理」</span></strong><br/></section><section><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;\">哨兵模式是在Redis主从集群的基础上加入了哨兵节点，监控主节点和从节点的状态。当Master节点出现故障时，哨兵节点会</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">自动从剩余的Slave节点中选举出一个新的Master节点</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;\">，并通知其他Slave节点和客户端。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">&nbsp;高可用性</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：提供故障的自动处理能力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">&nbsp;容灾恢复</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在主从模式数据备份的基础上，提供容错和自动恢复机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>读写分离</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提升读取性能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>解决了单点故障</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">：监测到master节点故障，会自动从slave节点中选出一个节点将其切换成master节点，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">在选举结束之前，redis会开启保护机制，禁止写操作</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，直到新的master节点产生。每个哨兵节点都是一个独立的进程，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">哨兵节点之间也会互相监控</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">1. 依然没有实现数据分片，无法在线扩容，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">2. 每个从节点和主节点的耦合度高，在主节点宕机到重新选举Master的期间，服务不可用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">3. 集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;单个主节点承担所有写操作，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「哨兵模式的应用场景」</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">适用于数据备份、容灾恢复，高可用性、小规模数据处理的场景。</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471444.png\" width=\"678\" height=\"248\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: 248px;\"/></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">集</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">群（Cluster）模式</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 171, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">「Cluster的原理」</span></strong></section><section><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在Redis Cluster中，引入slot槽来实现数据分片，slot的整体取值范围是0~16383，每个节点会分配一个slot区间，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">数据分散在多个节点上。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">每个分片都是由一个Redis主机和多个从机组成</span></strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">分片和分片之间是相互平行的</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">每个master节点负责维护一部分槽</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">以及</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">槽所映射的键值数据</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在Redis Cluster中，数据被分为<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">16384个槽，每个槽存储一部分数据。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 140, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">数据分片</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.578px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">是用CRC16算法对key进行hash操作，哈希计算的结果是16位的哈希值，将哈希值对16384取模，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">得到槽位编号。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">当存取Key的时候，根据<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: left;\">槽位编号，</span>找到对应的节</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">点进行数据的读写。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 171, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">「Cluster的优点」</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\">数据分片</span></strong>：<span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">基于slot槽的数据分片</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">，突破单节点的内存限制，</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">实现更大规模的数据分布式存储。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>横向扩展</strong></span><span style=\"word-spacing: 2px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">：实现在线动态横向扩缩容。<br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);\"><strong>高可用性</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">：每个分片都是一个主节点对应多</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.034em; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">个从节点，