nospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 201, 176); line-height: 26px;\">cd</span>&nbsp;redis-6.2.9<br/></code></pre><p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698473213.png\" style=\"text-wrap: wrap; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"/></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><li><section>编译</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">make&nbsp;<br/></code></pre><p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698473214.jpeg\" style=\"text-wrap: wrap; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"/></p><h4 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px;\">【步骤三】:运行Redis的测试套件（可选）</h4><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>注意:可能要花费几分钟</strong></p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">make&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 201, 176); line-height: 26px;\">test</span><br/></code></pre><h4 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px;\">【步骤四】:安装Redis到系统目录</h4><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consol